OL,6,FAround 100 will be lost in south Wales
OL,7,Fas a window company has gone into
OL,8,Fadministration.
OL,10,FEverest Glazing went into
OL,11,Fadministration on the 24th of April,
OL,12,Fand will close it's in , and office in.
OL,14,FIt comes 6 months after another
OL,15,Femployer in the area, , announced 500
OL,16,Fwould be lost at the nearby sites at
OL,17,FTreorchy, Llwynypia, Williamstown and
OL,18,FTaff's Well.
