OL,6,FAdministrators ReSolve said they had
OL,7,F"regrettably" made the decision to
OL,8,Fmake staff redundant and were now in
OL,9,Ftalks to explore an asset sale which
OL,10,Fwould help it fulfil existing customer
OL,11,Fcontracts and orders with Everest.
OL,13,FIan Smith is a workplace organiser at
OL,14,FEverest, and has worked there for 24
OL,15,Fyears.
OL,17,FHe says workers were told yesterday
OL,18,Fthat their jobs "are no longer. We
OL,19,Fwere made redundant from 5 o'clock
OL,20,Fyesterday afternoon, so just chucked
OL,21,Fon the scrapheap to be honest.
