OL,6,F'We feel that we've been treated like
OL,7,Fdogs.
OL,9,F"It's devastating. For the area we're
OL,10,Fin at the top end of the valleys, jobs
OL,11,Fare very scarce.
OL,13,F"We feel let down by Everest really,
OL,14,Fthere are boys here that have worked
OL,15,Fhere for 35 years.
OL,17,F"We're still waiting for last week's
OL,18,Fwages.
