OL,6,F"The boys have been down the job
OL,7,Fcentre this morning and said it was
OL,8,Flike walking into work because there
OL,9,Fwere so many faces from here."
OL,11,FThe GMB Union's regional organiser
OL,12,FGareth Morgans said the closure is "a
OL,13,Fdevastating blow to the upper Rhondda
OL,14,FValley, so soon after the closure of
OL,15,FUK windows and doors."
OL,17,F"The lives of our members working
OL,18,Fthere have been thrown into flux, but
OL,19,Fthe GMB family will help and support
OL,20,Fthem through these difficult months.
