OL,6,F"We will also be exploring the option
OL,7,Fof taking out a claim for the
OL,8,Fcompany's failure to consult with
OL,9,Fmembers before closing."
OL,11,FIn a statement administrators ReSolve
OL,12,Fsaid they had "assessed all options
OL,13,Favailable to Everest, including a
OL,14,Fpossible sale to interested parties.
OL,16,F"Unfortunately, it was not possible to
OL,17,Ffinalise a sale of the business as a
OL,18,Fgoing concern and therefore
OL,19,Fregrettably the administrators had to
OL,20,Fmake the majority of Everest 2020
OL,21,Fstaff redundant on April 29.
