OL,6,F"The administrators are now in
OL,7,Fadvanced talks with interested parties
OL,8,Fto explore the possibility of an asset
OL,9,Fsale that would help secure existing
OL,10,Fcustomer contracts and fulfil customer
OL,11,Forders. A further announcement will be
OL,12,Fmade in due course."
OL,14,FHeledd Fychan, MS for South Wales
OL,15,FCentral has tabled a question to the
OL,16,FCabinet Secretary asking "how Welsh
OL,17,FGovernment has supported the company
OL,18,Fand also what support will be
OL,19,Favailable to those affected."
