OL,6,FShe said in a statement, "Alternative
OL,7,Femployment is hard to come by in the
OL,8,Farea, and many people are struggling
OL,9,Fto make ends meet.
OL,11,F"The Welsh Government must take action
OL,12,Fto ensure more employment
OL,13,Fopportunities are created, and
OL,14,Festablish if any other businesses are
OL,15,Fstruggling and at risk of closure so
OL,16,Fsteps can be taken to prevent further
OL,17,Flosses."
